hadiths[120]{hadithnumber,text}:
3251,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina Munawra tashrif laye to log jaldi jaldi aap ki khidmat mein hazir honey lagey aur (galiyon bazaron mein aam log) kehney lagey : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif ley aaye. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif ley aaye. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif ley aaye. teen baar (kaha). main bhi logon key sath ziyaarat key liye hazir huwa. jab mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key chehra aqdas par tawajjoh sey nazar dali to mujhey malum ho gaya ke aap ka chehra kisi jhoot bolney waley ka chehra nahin. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka jo irshad mainey sab sey pehley suna, wo ye tha : aey logo ! salam aam karo, khana khilaya karo, sila rahmi karo, aur jab log so rahey hon to tum raat ko namaz (tahajjud) padho, tum salamti key sath jannat mein dakhil ho jaogey."
3252,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : salam aam karo, khana khilao , aur jis tarah Allah ney tumhen hukm diya hai is tarah bhai bhai bin kar raho."
3253,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, eik aadmi ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! Islam ka kon sa amal behtar hai? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye ke to khana khilaaey aur jisey to janta hai usey bhi salam karey aur jisey nahin janta usey bhi salam kerey."
3254,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik aadmi ka khana do key liye kafi hota hai. do aadmiyon ka khana chaar afrad key liye kafi hota hai. aur chaar afrad ka khana aath afrad key liye kafi hota hai."
3255,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik aadmi ka khana do key liye kafi hota hai aur do afrad ka khana teen aur chaar key liye kafi hota hai aur chaar aadmiyon ka khana paanch chhe afrad key liye kafi hota hai."
3256,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : momin eik aant mein khata hai aur kafir saat aanton mein khata hai."
3257,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kafir saat aanton mein khata hai aur momin eik aant mein khata hai."
3258,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : momin eik aant mein khata hai aur kafir saat aanton mein khata hai."
3259,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kabhi khaney mein aeb nahin nikala. agar pasand hota to kha letey warna chhod detey. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney is maana main eik aur hadees apney doosrey ustad Abu-Bakar bin Abi Sheeba (Rahimahullah) ki sanad sey bhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey bayan ki hai. Imam Abu-Bakar bin Abi Sheeba (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : sanad mein hamara ikhtilaf hai. wo Hazrat Abu-Hurera key shagrid (Abu Yahyaa ki bajaey) Abu-Haazim sey bayan kartey hain."
3260,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis ko ye baat pasand ho ke Allah Taala uskey ghar mein ziyada barkat dey, usey chahiye ke jab khana pesh kiya jaey aur jab (farigh honey key baad) khana uthaya jaey to wuzu karey."
3261,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baitulkhalaa sey bahar tashrif laye. aap ki khidmat mein khana pesh kiya gaya. eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya main aap ki khidmat mein wuzu key liye pani pesh na karun? aap ney farmaya : kya main namaz padhney ka iraada rakhta hun?
3262,"Hazrat Abu-Juhaifa (Wahab bin Abdullah) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main tek laga kar nahin khata."
3263,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Basar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey eik bakri Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hadiye key tor par pesh ki, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghutnon key bal beth kar khaney lagey. eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) ney (tajjub sey) kaha : bethney ka ye kaisa andaz hai? aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney mujhey shareef banda banaya hai, mutakabbir aur sarkash nahin banaya."
3264,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney chhe as-haab key sath khana tanaawul farma (khaa) rahey they. eik Erabi (dehati) (baddoo) aaya, wo (sara khana) do luqmon mein kha gaya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar ye shakhs Bismillah padh leta to khana tumharey liye kafi ho jata, chunanche tum mein sey jo shakhs khana khaye usey chahiye ke Bismillah padh ley. agar shuru mein Bismillah padhna bhool jaey to (yaad aaney par) yun keh ley : ( بِسْمِ اللهِ فِيْ أَوَّلِهِ وَآخِرِه ), ''Allah key naam key sath (khana shuru karta hun) uskey shuru aur uskey aakhir mein."
3265,"Hazrat umr bin Abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main khana kha raha tha to mujh sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ka naam ley (Bismillah padh)."
3266,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey har eik ko chahiye ke daain haath sey khaye , daain haath sey piye , daain haath sey ley aur daain haath sey dey kyonkey shetan baaein hath sey khata hai, baaein hath sey peeta hai, baaein hath sey deta aur baaein hath sey leta hai."
3267,"Hazrat umr bin Abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki kafalat mein parwarish paney wala eik bachcha tha. (eik din khana khatey huye) mera haath plate mein (idhar-udhar) ghoom raha tha to aap ney mujh sey farmaya : bachchey ! Allah ka naam lo (Bismillah padho), daain haath sey khao aur apney qarib sey khao."
3268,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : baaein hath sey na khaya karo kyonkey shetan baaein hath sey khata hai."
3269,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi shakhs khana khaye to apna haath na poonchhey jab tak usey chaat na ley , ya chatwaa na ley . Sufiyan bin Uena (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : mainey Imran bin Qais ko Amr bin Dinar sey sawal kartey huye suna , unhoney puchha : Ata ki is hadees ( لَا يَمْسَحُ أَحَدُكُمْ يَدَهُ حَتّٰي يَلْعَقَهَا أَوْ يُلْعِقَهَا ) key barey mein aap ka kya khayal hai ke wo kis (Sahaba) sey marvi hai? Amr bin Dinar ney kaha : Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey . umr bin Qais ney kaha : hamein ye hadees Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey bayan ki gaee hai. Amr bin Dinar ney kaha : Hazrat Jabir key hamarey paas aaney sey pehley hamney ye hadees Ata an ibne-Abbas sey yad ki hui hai. aur Ata (Rahimahullah) ney Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey us saal mulaqat ki hai jab Makka mein wo unkey paas muqeem they."
3270,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi shakhs apna haath na poonchhey jab tak usey chaat na ley kyonkey usey malum nahin ke khaney key kis hissey mein barkat hai."
3271,"Hazrat Umme Aasim (Rahimahullah) Alaiha sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key azad karda Hazrat Nabeesa bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey yahan tashrif laye jabke hum eik piyaley mein khana kha rahey they. unhoney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs piyaley mein khana khaye , phir us (piyaley) ko chaat ley to piyala uskey liye maghfirat ki dua karta hai."
3272,"Hazrat Abul Yamaan Mualla bin Rashid (Rahimahullah) apni daadi (Umme Aasim) (Rahimahullah) Alaiha sey riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney qabila Huzail key eik sahab Hazrat Nabeesa Al Khair (Raziallahu anhu) key barey mein bayan kartey huye farmaya : hum eik piyaley mein khana kha rahey they ke Nabeesa (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif ley aaye. unhoney kaha : hum sey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney bayan farmaya : jo shakhs piyaley mein khana kha kar usey chaatta hai, piyala uskey liye maghfirat ki dua karta hai."
3273,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab dastar khuwan par khana laga diya jaey to aadmi ko apney samney sey khana chahiye, apney sathi key aagey sey na khaye."
3274,"Hazrat Ikrash bin Zuweb (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat main eik bada piyaala pesh kiya gaya jis mein bahut sa sareed aur chiknai thi. hum log is mein sey khaney lagey to mera haath is mein har taraf ghoom raha tha. aap ney farmaya : Ikrash ! eik jagah sey khao, ye eik hi khana hai. phir hamarey samney eik thaal rakha gaya jis mein mukhtalif qism ki tazi khajuren thin. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka haath thaal mein ghoomney laga aur aap ney (mujh sey) farmaya : aey Ikrash ! jahan sey chaho khao, ye eik hi qisam nahin."
3275,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Basar (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat main eik piyala pesh kiya gaya to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : iskey kinaron sey khao. iski choti chhod do, is mein barkat dali jaeygi."
3276,"Hazrat Waasila Isqaa' Laisi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney sareed ki choti par haath rakh kar farmaya : Allah ka naam ley kar iskey kinaron sey khao aur iska ooncha (darmiyan wala) hissa rehney do (baad mein khana) kyonkey is mein barkat ooper sey aati hai."
3277,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab khana rakha jaey to uskey kinarey sey lo aur uska darmiyan chhod do kyonkey barkat uskey wast (beech) mein nazil hoti hai."
3278,"Hazrat Maaqil bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, wo khana kha rahey they ke itney mein un (key haath) sey eik luqma gir gaya. unhoney isey uthaya aur isey jo gardo-ghubar waghera lag gaya tha, usey door kiya, phir wo luqma kha liya. zaeemn-daaron ney eik doosrey ko isharey kiye (ke dekhen ye kya kar rahey hain). unhen kaha gaya : Allah Taala governer sahab (aap) ko durust rakhey , aap key luqma uthaney ki wajeh sey zameendaar eik doosrey ko isharey kartey hain jabke aap key samney ye khana mojud hai (phir gira huwa luqma na uthatey to kya harj tha, chahey khaa-m-khaah un logon key mazaq ka nishana baney). unhoney farmaya : main un ajmiyon ki wajeh sey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suni hui hadees par amal karna tarak nahin kar sakta. hum to, jab kisi ka luqma gir padta tha, usey hukm diya kartey they ke isey utha kar is par lagi hui chiz (tinkaa, ghubar waghera) door karey aur usey kha ley, aur isey shetan key liye na rehney dey."
3279,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey kisi key haath sey luqma gir padey to wo is par lagey gardo-ghubar ko saaf karey aur usey kha ley."
3280,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mardon mein sey bahut afrad kamil huye lekin aurton mein sey sirf Maryam binte Imran (Alaihissalam) aur Firon ki biwi Aasiya (Raziallahu anhu) kamil huin. aur Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ko dusri aurton par isi tarah fazilat hasil hai jis tarah sareed ko doosrey khaanon par fazilat hai."
3281,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aurton par Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki fazeelat aisey hi hai, jaisey doosrey khaanon par sareed ki fazilat hoti hai."
3282,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdulla (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein hamein khana kam milta tha. ziyada guzaara khajuron waghera par tha (phir jab hamein khana muyassar aata to hamarey paas ruomaal nahin hotey they, siwaye haathon , kalaaiyon aur paon key). haath ko lagi hui chiknai waghera is tarah idhar-udhar mal letey they. (phir) naya wuzu kiye baghair hi namaz padh letey they. Imam Ibne-Maja ney kaha : ye riwayat gharib hai. isey sirf Muhammad bin Salma ney bayan kiya hai."
3283,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab khana khatey they to farmatey they : ( الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ الَّذِي أَطْعَمَنَا , وَسَقَانَا وَجَعَلَنَا مُسْلِمِينَ ), ''Allah ka shukar hai jisney hamen khilaya, pilaya aur hamein musalman banaya."
3284,"Hazrat Abu-Umama Baahli (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key samney mojud khana (farigh honey par) uthaya jata to aap farmatey : ( الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ حَمْدًا كَثِيرًا , طَيِّبًا مُبَارَكًا , غَيْرَ مَكْفِيٍّ , وَلَا مُوَدَّعٍ , وَلَا مُسْتَغْنًى عَنْهُ رَبَّنَا ), ''tamam tareefen Allah hi key liye hain, aisi tareef jo bahut ziyada ho, pakizah ho aur is mein barkat di gaee ho, na kifaayat kiya gaya (ke mazeed ki zarurat na rahey), na ye aakhiri khana hai, na is sey be-niyazi ho sakti hai. aey hamarey rab ! ."""
3285,"Hazrat Muaz bin Anas Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney khana kha kar ye dua padhi : (الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ الَّذِي أَطْعَمَنِي هَذَا , وَرَزَقَنِيهِ مِنْ غَيْرِ حَوْلٍ مِنِّي , وَلَا قُوَّةٍ), ''har qism ki tareef Allah hi key liye jisney ye (khana) mujhey khilaya aur mujhey ye (khana) ata kiya baghair meri kisi taqat key aur baghair meri kisi quwat key.'' uskey guzishta (tamam) gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain."
3286,"Hazrat Wahshi bin Harab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Sahaba Raziallahu anhum ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum khana khatey hain to sair nahin hotey. aap ney farmaya : shayad tum log alag alag khatey ho? unhoney kaha : ji haan. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mil kar khana khaya karo aur is par Allah ka naam lo , tumharey liye is mein barkat ho jaeygi."
3287,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mil kar khao , alag alag na khao , kyonkey barkat jamaat (aur ijtamaaiyat) key sath hai."
3288,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khaney peeney ki chiz mein phunk nahin maartay they aur bartan mein saans nahin letey they."
3289,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab kisi key paas uska khaadim uska khana ley kar aaye to usey chahiye ke usey apney sath bithaaey aur wo (khaadim) us (Malik) key sath khaye. agar aisey nahin kar sakta to usey is mein sey kuchh (khana) dey dey."
3290,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab kisi ka ghulam usey khana pesh karey jiski (tayyari ki) mashaqqat aur (uskey liye aag ki) haraarat usney bardasht ki hai to usey bula kar apney sath khilaaey. agar ye na kar sakey to eik luqma ley kar uskey haath mein rakh dey."
3291,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey kisi ka khaadim uska khana laye to usey chahiye ke usey apney sath bithaaey ya usey thoda sa khana dey dey kyonkey usney uski garmi aur dhuwan bardasht kiya hai."
3292,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kabhi mez par rakh kar khana nahin khaya , aur na tashtari aur thaali mein. Qatada (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : phir log kis chiz par rakh kar khana khatey they? unhoney farmaya : dastar khuwan par."
3293,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kabhi mez par rakh kar khana khatey nahin dekha yahan tak key aap intiqal farma gaey."
3294,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney khana uthaey janey sey pehley uthney sey mana farmaya."
3295,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab dastar khuwan (par khana) laga diya jaey to koi aadmi (farigh ho kar) na uthey yahan tak key dastar khuwan uthaya jaey. aur apna haath na rokey agar-che sair ho gaya ho yahan tak key log farigh ho jaeyn. aur (agar usey zarurat na ho to) chahiye ke (apna) uzr bayan kar dey, kyonkey aadmi (haath rok kar) apney sathi ko sharminda kar deta hai aur wo bhi (sharam ki wajeh sey) haath rok leta hai. mumkin hai usey abhi khaney ki (mazeed) zarurat ho."
3296,"Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) binte Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is aadmi ko sirf khud hi ko malamat kerni chahiye jo is haal mein raat guzaarta hai ke uskey haath mein chiknai ki boo ho."
3297,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar koi shakhs is haal mein so gaya ke uskey haath mein chiknai ki boo thi aur usney haath nahin dhoya tha, phir usey koi takleef pahunch gaee to wo apney siwa kisi ko malamat na kerey."
3298,"Hazrat Asma binte Yazeed Ansaariya (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein khana hazir kiya gaya. aap ney hamein khaney ki pesh-kash ki. hamney kaha : hamein khahish nahin (bhook nahin hai). aap ney farmaya : bhook aur jhoot ko ikhatta na kiya karo."
3299,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) jinka talluq qabila banu Abdul-Ash'hal sey tha, un sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa to aap dophare (subah) ka khana kha rahey they. aap ney farmaya : aaiye , khana khaaiye. mainey kaha : main rozey sey hun. afsos ! kaash! main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key khaney mein sey kuchh kha leta."
3300,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Haris bin Juz Zubaidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamana Mubarak mein masjid mein gosht roti kha liya kartey they."
3301,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein chaltey chaltey kha letey they aur khadey ho kar pani pi liya kartey they."
3302,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kaddu pasand farmatey they."
3303,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : meri walida Umme Sulem (Raziallahu anha) ney merey haath khajuron ka eik tokraa Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bheja . aap mujhey (ghar mein) na miley. aap qarib hi apney eik azad karda ghulam key yahan tashrif ley gaey they. usney aap ko dawat di thi aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye khana tayyar kiya tha. main khidmat mein hazir huwa to aap khana tanaawul farma rahey they. aap ney mujhey bhi apney sath khana khaney ki dawat di. un Sahab ney kaddu aur gosht dal kar sareed bana rakha tha. mainey dekha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kaddu achchha lagta hai to main us (kaddu) key tukdey (bartan key atraaf mein sey) jama kar key aap key qarib karney laga. jab hum logon ney khana kha liya to aap wapis ghar tashrif ley gaey. mainey (khajuron ka) tokraa aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key samney rakh diya. aap ney khajuren khana aur taqseem karna shuru kar den yahan tak key khatam kar key farigh ho gaey."
3304,"Hazrat Hakim bin Jabir (Rahimahullah) apney walid (Hazrat Jabir bin Tariq Ahmasi (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key ghar mein dakhil huwa. aap key paas kaddu tha. mainey kaha : ye kya chiz hai? aap ney farmaya : ye kaddu hai, ye kaddu hai. hum iskey sath apney khaney (salan) mein izafa kartey hain."
3305,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : gosht duniya walon key aur jannat walon key khaanon ka sardar hai."
3306,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jab bhi gosht ki dawat di gaee , aap ney qubul farmaai. aur jab bhi aap ki khidmat mein gosht bator hadiya pesh kiya gaya, aap ney qubul farmaya."
3307,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein gosht laya gaya . aap ko (us mein sey) zaraa'a (dasti) ka gosht pesh kiya gaya jo aap ko bahut pasand tha. aap ney is mein sey daanton sey noch kar khaya."
3308,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Jaafar Taiyaar (bin Abi Talib) (Raziallahu anhuma) ney Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhuma) ko ye hadees sunai, jabke unhoney logon key liye eik oont zibeh kiya tha, ke unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey us waqt ye irshad Mubarak suna jab Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum Rasul Allah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko gosht pesh kar rahey they (khana khatey waqt har Sahaba umda umda gosht Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko pesh kar raha tha ke ye tanaawul farmaeyn, ye tukda lein, ye ziyada achcha hai). tab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farma rahey they : sab sey umda gosht pusht ka gosht hota hai."
3309,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main nahin janta ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kabhi Salim bhuni hui bakri dekhi ho yahan tak ke aap Allah key paas chaley gaey."
3310,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key samney sey kabhi bacha huwa bhuna gosht nahin uthaya gaya (sath khaney waley as-haab hotey they). gosht itna hi hota tha jo us waqt kha liya jaey. (aur na kabhi aap key sath bichhaney key liye qalin aur ghaleecha ley jaya gaya) ke jahan tashrif rakhna chahen, is par tashrif rakhen, balke waqt par jaisa bichhona muyassar hota saada ya umda, is par tashrif rakhtey.)"
3311,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Haris bin Juz Zubaidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath masjid mein khana khaya jo bhuna huwa gosht tha. phir hum (zameen par bichhi hui) kankariyon sey haath poonchh kar namaz padhney uth khadey huye aur hamney (naya) wuzu nahin kiya."
3312,"Hazrat Abu-Masood (Aqba bin Amr Ansari) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur aap sey baat karney laga. (Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key roab ki wajeh sey) uskey kandhey kaanpne lagey (us par kapkapi taari ho gaee) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ghabraao mat, main badshah nahin hun. main to eik aisi (aam si gharib) aurat ka beta hun jo khushk kiya huwa gosht khaya karti thi. Imam Abu-Adbullah Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : riwayat key Raavi Ismail (bin Abu-Khalid) hi ney isey mausool bayan kiya hai."
3313,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log (gaaey ya bakri key) paey sanbhaal rakhtey they, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qurbani sey pandarah din baad unhein tanaawul farmatey (khaate)."
3314,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hamarey liye do mari hui cheezen aur do khoon halal hain. murda cheezen to machli aur tiddi hain aur do khoon kaleji aur tilli hain."
3315,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumharey salan ka sardar namak hai."
3316,"Ummul-mominin sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sirka achchha salan hai."
3317,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sirka achchha salan hai."
3318,"Hazrat Umme Saad (Jameela binte Saad bin Rabee Ansaariya (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Ummul-mominin Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) key yahan tashrif laye jabkey main bhi unkey paas thi. aap ney farmaya : koi khana hai? Ummul-mominin ney farmaya : hamarey paas roti , khajuren aur sirka hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sirka achchha salan hai. aey Allah ! sirkey mein barkat ata farma. ye mujh sey pehley anbiya ka salan tha. jis ghar mein sirka ho wo gharib nahin."
3319,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : zaitun ka tel salan key tor par istimal karo aur isey (sar aur badan mein) lagao. ye Mubarak darkht sey hasil hota hai."
3320,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : zaitun ka tel khao (khurak mein istemaal karo) aur isey (sar aur badan mein) lagao kyonkey ye Mubarak (barkat wala) hai."
3321,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein jab doodh pesh kiya jata to farmatey : eik barkat ya do barkaten."
3322,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisey Allah Taala koi khana khaney ko dey to usey chahiye ke yun kahey : ( اللَّهُمَّ ! بَارِكْ لَنَا فِيهِ , وَارْزُقْنَا خَيْرًا مِنْهُ ), ''aey Allah ! hamin is mein barkat dey, aur is sey behtar rizq ata farma.'' aur jisey Allah Taala doodh peeney ko dey to usey yun kehna chahiye : (اللَّهُمَّ بَارِكْ لَنَا فِيهِ وَزِدْنَا مِنْهُ), ''aey Allah ! hamein is mein barkat dey, aur ye ziyada dey.'' kyonkey main nahin janta ke doodh key ilawa bhi koi chiz ghiza aur mashrub (dono) ka faeyda deti hai."
3323,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko meethi chiz aur shehad pasand tha.
3324,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : meri walida (Hazrat Umme Rumaan Zenab (Raziallahu anha)) mujhey mota karney ki tadbeer karti thin taake meri rukhsati kar key Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein rawana karen. lekin (kisi tadbeer sey) ye maqsad hasil na huwa yahan tak key mainey taaza khajuron key sath kakdi khai to intehai mutnaasib andaz ki farba ho gaee."
3325,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Jaafar (bin abi Talib) (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko taza khajoor key sath kakdi khatey dekha."
3326,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tarbuz key sath taza khajuren khatey they."
3327,"Ummul-mominin sayeda Aaysha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis ghar mein khajuren na hon, us ghar waley bhookey hain."
3328,"Hazrat Sulami (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis ghar mein khajuren na hon, wo us ghar ki tarah hai jis mein koi khana na ho."
3329,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein jab pehla phal pesh kiya jata to aap farmatey (اللَّهُمَّ بَارِكْ لَنَا فِي مَدِينَتِنَا , وَفِي ثِمَارِنَا , وَفِي مُدِّنَا , وَفِي صَاعِنَا , بَرَكَةً مَعَ بَرَكَةٍ), ''aey Allah ! hamarey shehar mein , hamarey phalon mein , hamarey mudd mein aur hamarey saa mein barkat key sath barkat ata farma.''phir khidmat mein hazir bachchon mein sey sab sey chhotey bachey ko wo phal waghera inayat farma detey."
3330,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : taza paki hui khajoor khushk khajoor key sath mila kar khaya karo. puraney (phal) ko naey key sath mila kar khao. (is sey) shetan ko ghussa aata hai aur wo kehta hai : Adam ka beta jeetaa raha yahan tak key usney naee chiz key sath purani chiz bhi khai."
3331,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney is baat sey mana farmaya ke aadmi apney sathiyon sey ijazat liye baghair do do khajuren mila kar khaye."
3332,"Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key azad karda Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu), jo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat kiya kartey they, aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko un ki baaten achchhi lagti thin, un sey riwayat hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney do do khajuren mila kar khaney sey mana farmaya."
3333,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey dekha ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein purani khajuren pesh ki gaeen to aap in ko (andar sey) saaf karney lagey."
3334,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Basar Sulami (Raziallahu anhuma) aur Hazrat Atiya bin Basar Sulami (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahan tashrif laye. hamney aap key bethney key liye (zameen par) eik chadar dal di. aap is par beth gaey. tab hamarey ghar mein Shaan wale Allah ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par ""wahi"" nazil farmaai. hamney aap ki khidmat mein makkhan aur khushk khajuren pesh kin. aur aap ko makkhan bahut pasand tha. aap par Allah ki rahmatein hon aur salam ho."
3335,"Hazrat abu-Haazim (Salma bin Dinar) (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Sehal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhuma) sey sawal kya : kya aap ney medey ki roti dekhi hai? unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat tak medey ki roti nahin dekhi thi . mainey kaha : kya Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein logon key paas chhalniyaan hoti thin? unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat tak chhalni nahin dekhi. mainey kaha : phir aap log jo (jo ka aata) baghair chhaaney kaisey kha letey they? unhoney kaha : haan! hum log is mein phunk maar letey they. jo (bhoosi ya chhaan) udna hota, ud jata. jo reh jata hum usey bhigo letey (aur aata goondh kar roti pakka letey.)"
3336,"Hazrat Umme Aiman (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney aata chhan kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye roti tayyar ki to aap ney farmaya : ye kya hai? unhoney arz kya : ye khana hum apney ilaqey mein banaya kartey hain. mera ji chaha ke aap key liye bhi is qism ki eik roti pakka dun. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : isko dobara aatey mein dal do, phir gundho."
3337,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney medey ki roti (khana to darkinar) apni eik aankh sey bhi nahin dekhi yahan tak ke aap Allah key paas chaley gaey."
3338,"Hazrat Ata (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) apney logon sey milney (ghaaliban Yuna basti mein) gaey. un logon ney aap ki khidmat mein pehley paki hui badi badi bareek rotiyaan pesh kin to aap ro diye aur farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye roti kabhi apni aakhon sey dekhi bhi nahin ."
3339,"Hazrat Qatada (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : hum log Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hotey , aur aap ka naan baai khada hota aur (hadees key Raavi) Daari bayan kartey hain ke aap ka dastarkhaan bicha huwa hota. eik din aap ney farmaya : khao, main nahin janta ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney , Allah key paas chaley janey tak, kabhi patli chapati ya Salim bhuni hui bakri apni aankh sey dekhi bhi ho (khaney ka to kya zikr.)"
3340,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : hamney Faaluzaj ka naam sab sey pehley us waqt suna jab Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas aa kar farmaya : aap ki ummat ko zamin mein futuhat hasil hongi, aur unhein duniya kasrat sey hasil hogi yahan tak key wo Faaluzaj khaeyngey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Faaluzaj kya hota hai? Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ney farmaya : wo ghi aur shehad dono ko mila dengey. ye sun kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aahista aawaz sey ro diye."
3341,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, eik din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mera ji chahta hai ke hamarey paas bhuri gehun ki safed roti hoti jis mein ghi mila huwa hota, hum usey khatey. eik Ansari ney ye baat suni aur aisi roti tayyar kar key aap ki khidmat mein pesh kar di. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye ghi kis chiz mein rakha huwa tha? usney kaha : saandey ki (khaal sey bani hui) kuppi mein. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye roti khaney sey inkar kar diya."
3342,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Umme Sulem (Raziallahu anha) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye eik roti tayyar ki jis mein kuch ghi dal diya tha, phir (mujhey) kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas jao aur unhein bula lao. mainey khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kya : ammi jaan aapko bula rahi hain. to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uth khadey huye, aur aap ki khidmat mein jo afrad hazir they un (sab) sey kaha : chalo. main un sey pehley ammi jaan key paas pahunch gaya aur unhein bataya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tamam sathiyon key sath tashrif la rahey hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif ley aaye aur farmaya : tum ney jo ( khana) tayyar kya hai, ley aao . meri walida ney arz kya : wo to mainey sirf aap key liye tayyar kya hai. aap ney farmaya : wohi ley aao . phir farmaya : aey Anas ! das das aadmiyon ko andar merey paas bulao . Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : main das das aadmiyon ko andar bulata raha (aur har group khana kha kar nikalta raha.) un sab ney sair ho kar kha liya. aur wo assi afrad they."
3343,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kabhi teen din musalsal gehun ki roti pet bhar kar nahin khai yahan tak key Allah azz-w-jall ney aap ko wafat dey di."
3344,"ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key ehle-khana ney (hijrat kar key) Madina aaney sey ley kar aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat tak kabhi musalsal teen raaten gehun ki roti sair ho kar nahin khai."
3345,"ummul-mominin sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) faut huye to merey ghar mein insan key khaney ki koi chiz na thi magar thodey sey jo meri taand par padey huye they. mein is mein sey (ley ley kar) khati rahi yahan tak key kafi muddat guzar gaee. (aakhir) mainey unhein maap liya to wo (jald hi) khatam ho gaey ."
3346,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key ehle-khana ney kabhi jo ki roti sair ho kar nahin khai yahan tak key aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) faut ho gaey ."
3347,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par musalsal kaee-kaee raaten aisi aati thin ke aap khaali pet raat guzaartey they, aur aap key ghar walon ko bhi raat ka khana muyassar nahin hota tha, jabkey us waqt logon ki aam ghiza jo ki roti hoti thi ."
3348,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) oon ka libas aur pewand laga joota pehan letey they. aur farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mota khaya aur mota pahna. Hasan (Rahimahullah) sey puchha gaya : mota khaney sey kya murad hai? unhoney farmaya : jo ki moti roti jo pani key ghoont key baghair halaq sey nichey nahin utarti thi ."
3349,"Hazrat Miqdam bin Madi karb (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aadmi pet sey bura koi bartan nahin bharta . aadmi ko to chand luqmey kafi hain jin sey uski kamar sidhi rahey . agar aadmi par uska nafs ghalib aa jaey (aur wo ziyada khana chahey) to eik tihai khaney key liye, eik tihai peeney key liye aur eik tihai saans key liye (rakh ley.)"
3350,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mojudgi main eik aadmi ney dakaar li to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apni dakarein rok lo. qiyamat key din wohi log ziyada taweel bhook bardasht kerengey jo duniya mein ziyada sair hotey hain.
3351,"Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, un sey eik khana khaney par israr kya gaya to unhoney farmaya : (jitna kha liya wohi) kafi hai. mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad Mubarak suna hai : duniya mein ziyada sair honey waley log qiyamat key din ziyada taweel arsey tak bhookey rahengey."
3352,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye bhi fuzul kharchi hai ke to har wo chiz khaye jiski tujhey khahish ho."
3353,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghar tashrif laye to (roti ka) eik tukda ( zamin par) gira huwa dekha. aap ney usey uthaya, saaf kya aur kha liya. phir farmaya : aey Aaisha! izzat waley (rizq) ka ehtiraam kar. ye jin logon key paas sey chala jata hai, dobara unkey paas nahin aata ."
3354,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : aey Allah ! main bhook sey teri panah mein aata hun, wo bistar ki buri sathi hai. aur khayanat sey teri panah mein aata hun, wo buri hum raz hai."
3355,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : raat ka khana mat chhodo , chahey mutthi bhar khajuren hi sahi , isliye ke uska chhod dena ( aadmi ko jald) boodha kar deta hai."
3356,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis ghar mein mehman aatey hain is mein bhalai us sey bhi ziyada jaldi aati hai jitni jaldi chhuri oont key kohan par chalti hai."
3357,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis ghar mein mehman khana khatey hain, is mein bhalai us sey bhi jald aati hai jitni jaldi chhuri oont key kohan par chalti hai."
3358,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye bhi sunnat hai ke aadmi mehman key sath ( usey rukhsat kartey waqt) ghar key darwazey tak aaye ."
3359,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey khana tayyar kya aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dawat di . Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye to ghar mein taswiren nazar aain, chunanche aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wapis chaley gaey ."
3360,Hazrat abu-Abdur-Rehman Safina (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki dawat ki. usney unkey liye khana tayyar kya. sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : kaash! hum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki bhi dawat kartey aur aap hamarey sath khana khatey. (is tajwiz key mutabiq) unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki dawat ki. aap tashrif laye aur apna haath darwazey ki chaukhat par rakha . aap ko ghar main eik taraf eik bareek parda nazar aaya to aap wapis lot gaey . Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : jaldi sey jaiye aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey arz kijiye : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap wapis kyon tashrif ley gaey? (Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key daryaft karney par) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : muzayyan ghar mein dakhil hona meri shaan key laaiq nahin .
3361,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, wo khana kha rahey they ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif ley aaye . unhoney majlis key ehtiraam waley maqam par unhen jagah di. (Hazrat umr beth gaey aur khana shuru kartey huye) farmaya : Bismillah, phir haath badha kar eik luqma liya, phir doosra luqma liya, phir farmaya : mujhey chiknai ka maza mehsus ho raha hai. aur ye chiknai gosht ki chiknai nahin (gosht mein thodi bahut charbi huwa hi karti hai.) Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kya : ameerul-mominin! main farba (janwer key) gosht ki talash mein, usey kharidney bazar gaya . mujhey wo mahngaa mehsus huwa . mainey eik dirham ka dubley (janwer key gosht) mein sey kharid liya ( jis mein charbi nahin thi .) aur is par eik dirham ka ghi dal liya . main chahta tha ke merey bachon ko eik eik haddi mil jaey . Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas jab bhi ye dono cheezen ( gosht aur ghi (jama ho jati thin, aap un mein sey eik tanaawul farmatey they aur dusri chiz sadqa kar detey they. Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : ameer ul-mominin! (ab to) tanaawul farmaiye. (aainda) merey paas jab bhi ye dono jama hongey, main bhi isi tarah kya karunga . Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main nahin khaaunga."
3362,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab to shorba tayyar karey to is mein pani ziyada dal liya kar. aur is mein sey kuch shorba apney padausiyon ko dey diya kar ."
3363,"Hazrat Maadaan bin abu-Talha Yamari Rahimahullah sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) Jumey key din khutba deney khadey huye . aap ney Allah ki hamd o sana key baad farmaya : aey logo! tum do paudey khatey ho, main to unhein bura hi samajhta hun, yani ye lehsun aur ye piyaz. mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein dekha hai ke agar kisi aadmi sey us (lehsun ya piyaz) ki bo mehsus hoti to uska haath pakad kar usey Baqee (key maidan) ki taraf nikal diya jata tha, isliye jisney zarur unhen khana ho, wo unhen pakka kar (un ki bu) khatam kar dey."
3364,"Hazrat Umme Ayub ansaariya (Raziallahu anha) (mezbane-Rasool abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ki ehliya) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye khana tayyar kya. is mein koi (nagawar bu wali) sabzi thi. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (wo khana) na khaya . aur farmaya : main apney sathi ( Jibril (Alaihissalam)) ko takleef dena pasand nahin karta ."
3365,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke chand afrad Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko un sey gandney ki bu mehsus hui. aap ney farmaya : kya mainey tumhen ye pauda khaney sey mana nahin kya tha? jis chiz sey insan ko eza (takleef) pahunchti hai us sey farishtey bhi eza (takleef) mehsus kartey hain.
3366,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir Johni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apney Sahaba Raziallahu anhum sey farmaya : piyaz na khaya karo. phir aahista sey ye lafz farmaya : kachcha na khao ."
3367,"Hazrat Salman Faarsi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ghi, paneer aur posteen key barey mein sawal kya gaya, aap ney farmaya : halal wo hai jo Allah ney apni kitab mein halal kya hai aur haram wo hai jo Allah ney apni kitab mein haram kya hai. aur jiskey barey mein khamoshi ikhtiyar farmaai hai, wo un chizon mein shamil hai jinkey barey mein Allah ney maafi dey di hai."
3368,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein Taaif key angoor hadiye key tor par pesh kiye gaey. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey bulaya aur farmaya : ye khosha ley lo aur apni walida key paas ley jao. mainey walida key paas pahunchaney sey pehley khud hi kha liya. phir kaee raaton key baad Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya is khoshey ka kya bana? kya tum ney wo apni walida ko pahuncha diya tha? mainey kaha : nahin. Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mera naam dhokey baaz rakh diya (mujhey dhokey baaz farmaya.)"
3369,"Hazrat Talha (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur aap key haath mein safar jal (bahi ka phal) tha. aap ney farmaya : aey Talha! ye ley lo, us sey dil ko rahat (aur quwat) hasil hoti hai."
3370,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney is baat sey mana farmaya ke aadmi chehrey key bal let kar khaye."
